Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,News from Northern Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.48,0:00:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I am simply to tell you that...\Nit has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Find Princess Cadance and Shining Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My dearest Twilight,\Nyou must come to Canterlot at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Season 3 | Episode 01\NThe Crystal Empire, Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed and Synced by GrayJeager\NFr.Jeager@Gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.91,0:01:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://www.youtube.com/user/GhxBronie\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.fr (french)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are all my quills?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, no... ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.02,0:01:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the Magical Compendium\Nvolumes 1 to 36! Where is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Flash cards!\NI should make some flash cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.54,0:01:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike, I'm gonna need you to quiz me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.71,0:01:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,On everything.\NEverything I've ever learned. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.38,0:01:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't gonna be enough cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, calm down.\NIt's just a test!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.28,0:01:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,JUST A TEST?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia wants\Nto give me some kind of exam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:02:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're trying to tell me to calm down\Nbecause... it's just a test?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.09,0:02:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.48,0:02:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say she's handling things\Npretty well, considering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't want me\Nto go as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadance and Shining Armor\Nare already there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The others will be joining them soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.43,0:02:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The empire's magic is powerful.\NIt cannot fall again, my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.69,0:02:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She will succeed at her task.\NAnd when she does,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll know she is that much closer\Nto being ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me, little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.03,0:02:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanted to see me?\NTo give me a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought my own quills.\NAnd plenty of paper to show my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a different kind of test.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Empire has returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I thought I'd studied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's anything\Nin any of my books--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There wouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Few remember it ever existed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Even my knowledge of\Nthe empire is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.57,0:03:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What I do know is that\Nit contains a powerful magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,One thousand years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,King Sombra, a unicorn\Nwhose heart was black as night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,took over the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He was ultimately overthrown,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,turned to shadow and banished\Nto the ice of the arctic north.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But not before he was able to\Nput a curse upon the empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,A curse that caused it\Nto vanish into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.61,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If the empire is filled with\Nhope and love,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,those things are reflected\Nacross all of Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If hatred and fear take hold...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I need your help\Nfinding a way to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to help protect\Nan entire empire?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It is, as I said, a different kind of test.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But one I'm certain you will pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,By joining Princess Cadance and\NShining Armor in the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He is. And your Ponyville friends\Nwill join you there as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have every confidence\Nyou will succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:04:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll know you are ready to move on\Nto the next level of your studies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if I fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.71,0:05:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't.\NBut Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,in the end, it must be you\Nand you alone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,who ultimately assists\NPrincess Cadance and Shining Armor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in doing what needs to be done\Nto protect the empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.92,0:05:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go. There is no time to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Twilight! That was fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess, you got a perfect score?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A minus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,B plus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! Did you... fail?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:06:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was prepared to do my best,\NThought I could handle any test {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For I can do so many tricks,\NBut I wasn't prepared for this {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Levitation would have been a breeze{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Facts and figures I recite with ease {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The square root\Nof five hundred and forty-six
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is twenty-three point three six six six\Nfour two eight nine one zero nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She is correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could ace a quiz on friendship's bliss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I wasn't prepared for this {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will I fail, or will I pass?\NI can't be sure...  {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She can't be sure... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mind is sharp, my skills intact\NMy heart is pure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Her heart is pure... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, I've taken my share of licks{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've made it through the thin and thick {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- But no I wasn't\N- Oh no, she wasn't {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- But no I wasn't\N- Oh no, she wasn't {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No I wasn't prepared for this! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.02,0:07:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, prepared for what exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.16,0:07:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna celebrate\Nyour awesomeness with Princess Celestia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to the Crystal Empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.05,0:08:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! And you all made fun of me\Nfor packing so many scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Shining Armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilie! You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We better get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things out here we really\Ndon't want to run into after dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just say the empire...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't the only thing that's returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Something keeps trying to get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We think it's the unicorn king\Nwho originally cursed the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But Princess Celestia said I was being sent\Nhere to find a way to protect the empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If King Sombra can't get in,\Nthen it must already be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's one of the things, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get to\Nthe Crystal Empire. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, Shining Armor,\Nyour horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sparklriffic!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gorgeous!\NAbsolutely gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no words!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.07,0:10:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus, Rarity.\NWe're here to help Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not admire the scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see what the big deal is.\NJust looks like another old castle to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Another old...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your mind?!\NLook at the magn--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Cadance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sunshine, sunshine, ladybugs awake,\Nclap your hooves and do a little shake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,One of these days,\Nwe need to get together
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,when the fate of Equestria\Nisn't hanging in the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.85,0:10:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cadance has been able to use her magic\Nto spread love and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems to be what is protecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But she hasn't slept, barely eats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help her, but my protection spell\Nhas been countered by King Sombra.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright Shining Armor, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not fine.\NShe can't go on like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.11,0:11:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And if her magic were to fade,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you saw what's out there\Nwaiting for that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.55,0:11:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why we're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,With Cadance putting all her strength\Ninto keeping her spell going,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and me trying to keep an eye\Non signs of trouble in the arctic,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,we haven't been able to gather\Nmuch information from the Crystal Ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Crystal Ponies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There are Crystal Ponies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But we have to believe one of them\Nknows how we can protect the empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,without having to use\NCadance's magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,A research paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be part of my test!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,To gather information from the\Ncrystal ponies and deliver it to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be great!\NI love research papers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, who doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohohoh! Lemme guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Spike?!\NNo no, Fluttershy! Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, big brother.\NI'm really good at this sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.05,0:12:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure? Absolutely sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.39,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I wish I could help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't seem to remember anything\Nbefore King Sombra came to power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't want to remember anything\Nabout the time he ruled over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,King Sombra's spell must be\Nwhy their coats aren't... crystally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we really been gone\Na thousand years?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like it was just yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think of anything,\Neven the smallest thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a total bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the others are having better luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A way to protect the empire!\NYou know anything about it or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could help you. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! You gotta know something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I don't have any information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um. Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello!\NI was just wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh that's okay.\NYou all look really busy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to gather some intel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.23,0:13:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It just feels like something is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.20,0:13:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks the same, but...\Nit doesn't feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A spy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A spy?!\NHow did they know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Must have noticed\Nmy night vision goggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.90,0:13:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Night vision-ey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you flip your mane,\Nit simply must create a rainbow of color.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't I look just magnificent?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So sparkly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I got nothing so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.18,0:14:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My cover has been blown.\NI repeat, my cover has been blown!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooookay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Twilight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,these crystal ponies seem to have\Nsome kinda collective amnesia or somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Only thing I was able to get out of 'em\Nwas somethin' about a library.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A library?\NWhy didn't you say so?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.49,0:14:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... thought I just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... I don't even know what to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no words.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.70,0:15:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We're looking for a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We have plenty of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.64,0:15:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You do. You really do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're lookin' for a history book.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Somethin' that may tells us how\Nthe empire might've protected itself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,from danger back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.\NHistory, history...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.37,0:15:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is where, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I can't seem to remember.\NI'm not sure I actually work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.63,0:15:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just take a look around.\NI'm sure we can find it on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me know if you find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I like her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone else startin' to think\Nthis is a lost cause?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no,\Nno...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,YES!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,History of the Crystal Empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope it has\Nthe answers we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A 'Crystal Fair'.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,According to this book,\Nit was established by their first queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and became their\Nmost important tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.94,0:16:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The fair was held every year to
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,renew the spirit of love\Nand unity in the empire
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so they could protect it from harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends and I could put it together.\NEverything we need to know is in the book!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds pretty promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get started right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike.\NWe've got a Crystal Fair to put together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Princess Cadance needs our help,\NHer magic will not last forever {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.19,0:17:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think we can do it,\NBut we need to work together {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have to get this right,\NYes we have to make them see {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can save the Crystal Ponies\Nwith their history {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It says that they like jousting {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They flew a flag of many hues {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Made sweets with crystal berries {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They had a petting zoo with tiny ewes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh we have to get this right,\NYes we have to make them see {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can save the Crystal Ponies\Nwith their history {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There was a crystal flugelhorn{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.70,0:17:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That everypony liked to play {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the Crystal Kingdom anthem {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you learn it in a day? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.71,0:18:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh we have to get this right,\NYes we have to make them see {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can save the Crystal Ponies{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With their history {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.35,0:18:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how\NI could have done this without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One last check to make sure\Neverything is in place,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the festivities can begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this thing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The last page of the book mentioned\Na Crystal Heart as the fair's centerpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I used my magic to cut one\Nout of a crystal block.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice work, Twi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Think we're ready to get\Nthis fair up and runnin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear ye, hear--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear ye, hear ye.\NPrincess Cadance
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and Prince Shining Armor\Ndo cordially
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,invite you to attend\Nthe Crystal Fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in, y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Got food and drinks thataway,\Ngames and crafts are thataway,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Crystal Heart to the back\Nnear the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We totally nailed it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be feeling a lot of love\Nand unity about now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna have some grub, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you picking?\NCrystal Empire berry pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe some crystal corn-on-the-cob!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:20:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is with these ponies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing all of this, I feel like\NI'm starting to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember things from before the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Crystal Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think they really have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't have a Crystal Fair\Nwithout the Crystal Heart, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.47,0:20:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole purpose of the Crystal Fair\Nis to lift the spirits of the Crystal Ponies,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,so the light within them\Ncan power the Crystal Heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the empire can be protected!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.99,0:20:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I do work at a library!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that about\N'powering the heart'?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't believe you found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,King Sombra said he'd hidden it away,\Nwhere we would never see it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I only hope it will still be\Nas powerful after all these years!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, funnelcake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.55,0:20:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we may have a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know it was an actual relic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The book didn't mention anything about\Nthe Crystal Ponies powering the Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a page missing...\Nhow did I not notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.10,0:21:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilie...
